2. **`spawnParticle`** â€” Emits decorative particles from random nodes at random angles
3. **`updateParticles`** â€” Moves particles, applies drag, and removes expired ones
4. **`smoothCamera`** â€” Lerps camera position toward a target (easing factor 0.06)
5. **`simulationTick`** â€” Main loop at ~60fps, spawning a particle every 3rd tick
